{{Otheruses|Banshee}}
'''''Banshee''''' was a pair of [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90]] [[Corvette/Legends|corvettes]] belonging to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. They, along with the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] [[Shrike (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Shrike'']], were [[Attack on the Shrike|destroyed]] by [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wings]], one of them [[Pilot/Legends|piloted]] by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]].

